1:1 paulov, apostolov ouk ap anyrwpwn, oude di anyrwpou,
 alla dia ihsou cristou kai yeou patrov tou egeirantov auton
 ek nekrwn,
1:2 kai oi sun emoi pantev adelfoi, taiv ekklhsiaiv thv
 galatiav:
1:3 cariv umin kai eirhnh apo yeou patrov kai kuriou hmwn
 ihsou cristou,
1:4 tou dontov eauton uper twn amartiwn hmwn, opwv exelhtai
 hmav ek tou enestwtov aiwnov ponhrou kata to yelhma tou
 yeou kai patrov hmwn,
1:5 w h doxa eiv touv aiwnav twn aiwnwn: amhn.

1:6 yaumazw oti outwv tacewv metatiyesye apo tou kalesantov
 umav en cariti cristou eiv eteron euaggelion,
1:7 o ouk estin allo, ei mh tinev eisin oi tarassontev umav
 kai yelontev metastreqai to euaggelion tou cristou.
1:8 alla kai ean hmeiv h aggelov ex ouranou euaggelizhtai
 umin par o euhggelisameya umin, anayema estw.
1:9 wv proeirhkamen, kai arti palin legw: ei tiv umav euaggelizetai
 par o parelabete, anayema estw.
1:10 arti gar anyrwpouv peiyw h ton yeon; h zhtw anyrwpoiv
 areskein; ei gar eti anyrwpoiv hreskon, cristou doulov
 ouk an hmhn.

1:11 gnwrizw de umin, adelfoi, to euaggelion to euaggelisyen
 up emou oti ouk estin kata anyrwpon:
1:12 oude gar egw para anyrwpou parelabon auto oute edidacyhn,
 alla di apokaluqewv ihsou cristou.
1:13 hkousate gar thn emhn anastrofhn pote en tw ioudaismw,
 oti kay uperbolhn ediwkon thn ekklhsian tou yeou kai eporyoun
 authn,
1:14 kai proekopton en tw ioudaismw uper pollouv sunhlikiwtav
 en tw genei mou, perissoterwv zhlwthv uparcwn twn patrikwn
 mou paradosewn.
1:15 ote de eudokhsen o yeov o aforisav me ek koiliav mhtrov
 mou kai kalesav dia thv caritov autou
1:16 apokaluqai ton uion autou en emoi, ina euaggelizwmai
 auton en toiv eynesin, euyewv ou prosaneyemhn sarki kai
 aimati,
1:17 oude anhlyon eiv ierosoluma prov touv pro emou apostolouv,
 alla aphlyon eiv arabian, kai palin upestreqa eiv damaskon.
1:18 epeita meta eth tria anhlyon eiv ierosoluma istorhsai
 petron, kai epemeina prov auton hmerav dekapente:
1:19 eteron de twn apostolwn ouk eidon ei mh iakwbon ton
 adelfon tou kuriou.
1:20 a de grafw umin, idou enwpion tou yeou oti ou qeudomai.
1:21 epeita hlyon eiv ta klimata thv suriav kai thv kilikiav.
1:22 hmhn de agnooumenov tw proswpw taiv ekklhsiaiv thv
 ioudaiav taiv en cristw:
1:23 monon de akouontev hsan oti o diwkwn hmav pote nun
 euaggelizetai thn pistin hn pote eporyei,
1:24 kai edoxazon en emoi ton yeon.

2:1 epeita dia dekatessarwn etwn palin anebhn eiv ierosoluma
 meta barnaba, sumparalabwn kai titon:
2:2 anebhn de kata apokaluqin: kai aneyemhn autoiv to euaggelion
 o khrussw en toiv eynesin, kat idian de toiv dokousin, mhpwv
 eiv kenon trecw h edramon.
2:3 all oude titov o sun emoi, ellhn wn, hnagkasyh peritmhyhnai,
2:4 dia de touv pareisaktouv qeudadelfouv, oitinev pareishlyon
 kataskophsai thn eleuyerian hmwn hn ecomen en cristw ihsou,
 ina hmav katadoulwswntai:
2:5 oiv oude prov wran eixamen th upotagh, ina h alhyeia
 tou euaggeliou diameinh prov umav.
2:6 apo de twn dokountwn einai ti, opoioi pote hsan ouden
 moi diaferei: proswpon yeov anyrwpou ou lambanei: emoi
 gar oi dokountev ouden prosaneyento,
2:7 alla tounantion idontev oti pepisteumai to euaggelion
 thv akrobustiav kaywv petrov thv peritomhv:
2:8 o gar energhsav petrw eiv apostolhn thv peritomhv enhrghsen
 kai emoi eiv ta eynh:
2:9 kai gnontev thn carin thn doyeisan moi, iakwbov kai
 khfav kai iwannhv, oi dokountev stuloi einai, dexiav edwkan
 emoi kai barnaba koinwniav, ina hmeiv eiv ta eynh, autoi
 de eiv thn peritomhn:
2:10 monon twn ptwcwn ina mnhmoneuwmen, o kai espoudasa
 auto touto poihsai.

2:11 ote de hlyen petrov eiv antioceian, kata proswpon
 autw antesthn, oti kategnwsmenov hn.
2:12 pro tou gar elyein tinav apo iakwbou meta twn eynwn
 sunhsyien: ote de hlyon, upestellen kai afwrizen eauton,
 foboumenov touv ek peritomhv.
2:13 kai sunupekriyhsan autw kai oi loipoi ioudaioi, wste
 kai barnabav sunaphcyh autwn th upokrisei.
2:14 all ote eidon oti ouk oryopodousin prov thn alhyeian
 tou euaggeliou, eipon tw petrw emprosyen pantwn: ei su
 ioudaiov uparcwn eynikwv zhv kai ouk ioudaikwv, ti ta eynh
 anagkazeiv ioudaizein;

2:15 hmeiv fusei ioudaioi kai ouk ex eynwn amartwloi,
2:16 eidotev [de] oti ou dikaioutai anyrwpov ex ergwn nomou
 ean mh dia pistewv ihsou cristou, kai hmeiv eiv criston
 ihsoun episteusamen, ina dikaiwywmen ek pistewv cristou
 kai ouk ex ergwn nomou, dioti ou dikaiwyhsetai ex ergwn
 nomou pasa sarx.
2:17 ei de zhtountev dikaiwyhnai en cristw eureyhmen kai
 autoi amartwloi, ara cristov amartiav diakonov; mh genoito.
2:18 ei gar a katelusa tauta palin oikodomw, parabathn emauton
 sunisthmi.
2:19 egw gar dia nomou nomw apeyanon, ina yew zhsw.
2:20 cristw sunestaurwmai: zw de ouketi egw, zh de en emoi cristov: o de
 nun zw en sarki, en pistei zw th tou uiou tou yeou tou agaphsantov me
 kai paradontov eauton uper emou.
2:21 ouk ayetw thn carin tou yeou: ei gar dia nomou dikaiosunh,
 ara cristov dwrean apeyanen.

3:1 w anohtoi galatai, tiv umav ebaskanen th alhyeia mh
 peiyesyai, oiv kat ofyalmouv ihsouv cristov proegrafh en
 umin estaurwmenov;
3:2 touto monon yelw mayein af umwn: ex ergwn nomou to pneuma
 elabete h ex akohv pistewv;
3:3 outwv anohtoi este; enarxamenoi pneumati nun sarki epiteleisye;
3:4 tosauta epayete eikh; ei ge kai eikh.
3:5 o oun epicorhgwn umin to pneuma kai energwn dunameiv
 en umin, ex ergwn nomou h ex akohv pistewv;
3:6 kaywv abraam episteusen tw yew, kai elogisyh autw eiv
 dikaiosunhn.
3:7 ginwskete ara oti oi ek pistewv, outoi eisin uioi abraam.
3:8 proidousa de h grafh oti ek pistewv dikaioi ta eynh
 o yeov, proeuhggelisato tw abraam oti eneuloghyhsontai
 en soi panta ta eynh.
3:9 wste oi ek pistewv eulogountai sun tw pistw abraam.
3:10 osoi gar ex ergwn nomou eisin, upo kataran eisin: gegraptai
 gar: epikataratov pav ov ouk emmenei en pasin toiv gegrammenoiv
 en tw bibliw tou nomou tou poihsai auta.
3:11 oti de en nomw oudeiv dikaioutai para tw yew, dhlon:
 oti o dikaiov ek pistewv zhsetai.
3:12 o de nomov ouk estin ek pistewv, all o poihsav auta
 anyrwpov zhsetai en autoiv.
3:13 cristov hmav exhgorasen ek thv katarav tou nomou genomenov
 uper hmwn katara: gegraptai gar: epikataratov pav o kremamenov
 epi xulou:
3:14 ina eiv ta eynh h eulogia tou abraam genhtai en cristw
 ihsou, ina thn epaggelian tou pneumatov labwmen dia thv
 pistewv.

3:15 adelfoi, kata anyrwpon legw: omwv anyrwpou kekurwmenhn
 diayhkhn oudeiv ayetei h epidiatassetai.
3:16 tw de abraam erreyhsan ai epaggeliai kai tw spermati
 autou: ou legei, kai toiv spermasin, wv epi pollwn, all
 wv ef enov, kai tw spermati sou, ov estin cristov.
3:17 touto de legw: diayhkhn prokekurwmenhn upo tou yeou
 eiv criston o meta eth tetrakosia kai triakonta gegonwv
 nomov ouk akuroi, eiv to katarghsai thn epaggelian.
3:18 ei gar ek nomou h klhronomia, ouketi ex epaggeliav:
 tw de abraam di epaggeliav kecaristai o yeov.
3:19 ti oun o nomov; twn parabasewn carin proseteyh, acri
 ou elyh to sperma w ephggeltai, diatageiv di aggelwn en
 ceiri mesitou.
3:20 o de mesithv enov ouk estin, o de yeov eiv estin.
3:21 o oun nomov kata twn epaggeliwn tou yeou; mh genoito.
 ei gar edoyh nomov o dunamenov zwopoihsai, ontwv an ek
 nomou hn h dikaiosunh:
3:22 alla sunekleisen h grafh ta panta upo amartian, ina
 h epaggelia ek pistewv ihsou cristou doyh toiv pisteuousin.

3:23 pro de tou elyein thn pistin upo nomon efrouroumeya
 sugkekleismenoi eiv thn mellousan pistin apokalufyhnai.
3:24 wste o nomov paidagwgov hmwn gegonen eiv criston, ina
 ek pistewv dikaiwywmen:
3:25 elyoushv de thv pistewv ouketi upo paidagwgon esmen.

3:26 pantev gar uioi yeou este dia thv pistewv en cristw
 ihsou:
3:27 osoi gar eiv criston ebaptisyhte, criston enedusasye.
3:28 ouk eni ioudaiov oude ellhn, ouk eni doulov oude eleuyerov,
 ouk eni arsen kai yhlu: pantev gar umeiv eiv este en cristw
 ihsou.
3:29 ei de umeiv cristou, ara tou abraam sperma este kai
 kat epaggelian klhronomoi.

4:1 legw de, ef oson cronon o klhronomov nhpiov estin, ouden
 diaferei doulou, kuriov pantwn wn,
4:2 alla upo epitropouv estin kai oikonomouv acri thv proyesmiav
 tou patrov.
4:3 outwv kai hmeiv, ote hmen nhpioi, upo ta stoiceia tou
 kosmou hmen dedoulwmenoi:
4:4 ote de hlyen to plhrwma tou cronou, exapesteilen o yeov
 ton uion autou, genomenon ek gunaikov, genomenon upo nomon,
4:5 ina touv upo nomon exagorash, ina thn uioyesian apolabwmen.
4:6 oti de este uioi, exapesteilen o yeov to pneuma tou
 uiou autou eiv tav kardiav umwn, krazon: abba o pathr.
4:7 wste ouketi ei doulov, all uiov: ei de uiov, kai klhronomov
 yeou dia cristou.

4:8 alla tote men ouk eidotev yeon edouleusate toiv mh
 fusei ousin yeoiv:
4:9 nun de gnontev yeon, mallon de gnwsyentev upo yeou,
 pwv epistrefete palin epi ta asyenh kai ptwca stoiceia,
 oiv palin anwyen douleuein yelete;
4:10 hmerav parathreisye kai mhnav kai kairouv kai eniautouv!
4:11 foboumai umav mhpwv eikh kekopiaka eiv umav.

4:12 ginesye wv egw, oti kagw wv umeiv, adelfoi, deomai
 umwn. ouden me hdikhsate.
4:13 oidate de oti di asyeneian thv sarkov euhggelisamhn
 umin to proteron,
4:14 kai ton peirasmon mou ton en th sarki mou ouk exouyenhsate
 oude exeptusate, all wv aggelon yeou edexasye me, wv criston
 ihsoun.
4:15 tiv oun hn o makarismov umwn; marturw gar umin oti
 ei dunaton touv ofyalmouv umwn exoruxantev an edwkate moi.
4:16 wste ecyrov umwn gegona alhyeuwn umin;
4:17 zhlousin umav ou kalwv, alla ekkleisai umav yelousin,
 ina autouv zhloute.
4:18 kalon de to zhlousyai en kalw pantote kai mh monon
 en tw pareinai me prov umav.
4:19 teknia mou, ouv palin wdinw, acri ou morfwyh cristov
 en umin!
4:20 hyelon de pareinai prov umav arti kai allaxai thn fwnhn
 mou, oti aporoumai en umin.

4:21 legete moi oi upo nomon yelontev einai: ton nomon ouk
 akouete;
4:22 gegraptai gar oti abraam duo uiouv escen, ena ek thv
 paidiskhv kai ena ek thv eleuyerav.
4:23 all o men ek thv paidiskhv kata sarka gegennhtai, o
 de ek thv eleuyerav dia thv epaggeliav.
4:24 atina estin allhgoroumena. autai gar eisin duo diayhkai,
 mia men apo orouv sina, eiv douleian gennwsa, htiv estin
 agar:
4:25 to gar agar sina orov estin en th arabia, sustoicei
 de th nun ierousalhm, douleuei de meta twn teknwn authv:
4:26 h de anw ierousalhm eleuyera estin, htiv estin mhthr
 pantwn hmwn.
4:27 gegraptai gar: eufranyhti steira h ou tiktousa, rhxon
 kai bohson h ouk wdinousa: oti polla ta tekna thv erhmou
 mallon h thv ecoushv ton andra.
4:28 hmeiv de, adelfoi, kata isaak epaggeliav tekna esmen.
4:29 all wsper tote o kata sarka gennhyeiv ediwken ton kata
 pneuma, outwv kai nun.
4:30 alla ti legei h grafh; ekbale thn paidiskhn kai ton
 uion authv: ou mh gar klhronomhsei o uiov thv paidiskhv
 meta tou uiou thv eleuyerav.
4:31 ara, adelfoi, ouk esmen paidiskhv tekna, alla thv
 eleuyerav.

5:1 th eleuyeria oun, h cristov hmav hleuyerwsen, sthkete,
 kai mh palin zugw douleiav enecesye.
5:2 ide egw paulov legw umin oti ean peritemnhsye, cristov
 umav ouden wfelhsei.
5:3 marturomai de palin panti anyrwpw peritemnomenw oti
 ofeilethv estin olon ton nomon poihsai.
5:4 kathrghyhte apo tou cristou oitinev en nomw dikaiousye,
 thv caritov exepesate:
5:5 hmeiv gar pneumati ek pistewv elpida dikaiosunhv apekdecomeya.
5:6 en gar cristw ihsou oute peritomh ti iscuei oute akrobustia,
 alla pistiv di agaphv energoumenh.
5:7 etrecete kalwv: tiv umav enekoqen th alhyeia mh peiyesyai;
5:8 h peismonh ouk ek tou kalountov umav.
5:9 mikra zumh olon to furama zumoi.
5:10 egw pepoiya eiv umav en kuriw oti ouden allo fronhsete:
 o de tarasswn umav bastasei to krima, ostiv an h.
5:11 egw de, adelfoi, ei peritomhn eti khrussw, ti eti diwkomai;
 ara kathrghtai to skandalon tou staurou.
5:12 ofelon kai apokoqontai oi anastatountev umav.

5:13 umeiv gar ep eleuyeria eklhyhte, adelfoi: monon mh
 thn eleuyerian eiv aformhn th sarki, alla dia thv agaphv
 douleuete allhloiv.
5:14 o gar pav nomov en eni logw plhroutai, en tw, agaphseiv
 ton plhsion sou wv seauton.
5:15 ei de allhlouv daknete kai katesyiete, blepete mh up
 allhlwn analwyhte.

5:16 legw de, pneumati peripateite kai epiyumian sarkov
 ou mh teleshte.
5:17 h gar sarx epiyumei kata tou pneumatov, to de pneuma
 kata thv sarkov: tauta de antikeitai allhloiv, ina mh a
 an yelhte tauta poihte.
5:18 ei de pneumati agesye, ouk este upo nomon.
5:19 fanera de estin ta erga thv sarkov, atina estin moiceia,
 porneia, akayarsia, aselgeia,
5:20 eidwlolatria, farmakeia, ecyrai, ereiv, zhloi, yumoi,
 eriyeiai, dicostasiai, aireseiv,
5:21 fyonoi, fonoi, meyai, kwmoi kai ta omoia toutoiv, a
 prolegw umin kaywv kai proeipon, oti oi ta toiauta prassontev
 basileian yeou ou klhronomhsousin.
5:22 o de karpov tou pneumatov estin agaph, cara, eirhnh,
 makroyumia, crhstothv, agaywsunh, pistiv,
5:23 praothv, egkrateia: kata twn toioutwn ouk estin nomov.
5:24 oi de tou cristou thn sarka estaurwsan sun toiv payhmasin
 kai taiv epiyumiaiv.
5:25 ei zwmen pneumati, pneumati kai stoicwmen.
5:26 mh ginwmeya kenodoxoi, allhlouv prokaloumenoi, allhloiv
 fyonountev.

6:1 adelfoi, ean kai prolhfyh anyrwpov en tini paraptwmati,
 umeiv oi pneumatikoi katartizete ton toiouton en pneumati
 praothtov, skopwn seauton, mh kai su peirasyhv.
6:2 allhlwn ta barh bastazete, kai outwv anaplhrwsate ton
 nomon tou cristou.
6:3 ei gar dokei tiv einai ti mhden wn, eauton frenapata.
6:4 to de ergon eautou dokimazetw ekastov, kai tote eiv
 eauton monon to kauchma exei kai ouk eiv ton eteron:
6:5 ekastov gar to idion fortion bastasei.
6:6 koinwneitw de o kathcoumenov ton logon tw kathcounti
 en pasin agayoiv.

6:7 mh planasye, yeov ou mukthrizetai: o gar ean speirh
 anyrwpov, touto kai yerisei:
6:8 oti o speirwn eiv thn sarka eautou ek thv sarkov yerisei
 fyoran, o de speirwn eiv to pneuma ek tou pneumatov yerisei
 zwhn aiwnion.
6:9 to de kalon poiountev mh ekkakwmen: kairw gar idiw yerisomen
 mh ekluomenoi.
6:10 ara oun wv kairon ecomen, ergazwmeya to agayon prov
 pantav, malista de prov touv oikeiouv thv pistewv.

6:11 idete phlikoiv umin grammasin egraqa th emh ceiri.
6:12 osoi yelousin euproswphsai en sarki, outoi anagkazousin
 umav peritemnesyai, monon ina mh tw staurw tou cristou
 diwkwntai.
6:13 oude gar oi peritetmhmenoi autoi nomon fulassousin,
 alla yelousin umav peritemnesyai, ina en th umetera sarki
 kauchswntai.
6:14 emoi de mh genoito kaucasyai ei mh en tw staurw tou
 kuriou hmwn ihsou cristou, di ou emoi kosmov estaurwtai
 kagw tw kosmw.
6:15 en gar cristw ihsou oute peritomh ti iscuei oute akrobustia,
 alla kainh ktisiv.
6:16 kai osoi tw kanoni toutw stoichsousin, eirhnh ep autouv
 kai eleov, kai epi ton israhl tou yeou.

6:17 tou loipou kopouv moi mhdeiv parecetw: egw gar ta stigmata
 tou kuriou ihsou en tw swmati mou bastazw.

6:18 h cariv tou kuriou hmwn ihsou cristou meta tou pneumatov
 umwn, adelfoi: amhn.
